  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Become a great BBQ 🍖 master! Cook delicious BBQs in nature with friends up to 5 people.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148010/extras/111dc9a16f1fd316b78fe3935083f9d0.avif?t=1759166534\" width=411 height=180 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 🍖<strong>Step-by-step</strong> creation of barbecue.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 🍖 <strong>Variability</strong> of recipes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148010/extras/6cde616f860bb561b1a21db56be835b4.poster.avif?t=1759166534\" width=640 height=640 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148010/extras/6cde616f860bb561b1a21db56be835b4.webm?t=1759166534\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148010/extras/6cde616f860bb561b1a21db56be835b4.mp4?t=1759166534\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>    </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 🍖 You will <strong>smell</strong> the BBQ through the monitor</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 🍖  You can <strong>kick</strong> annoying friends who are talking about simple things</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover the art of creating barbecues from many different ingredients: even take rabbit meat and marinate it in bananas in soy sauce! (It's joke)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And by the way, don't forget to enjoy the BBQ itself after cooking!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Become a great BBQ 🍖 master! Cook delicious BBQs in nature with friends up to 5 people.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148010/extras/111dc9a16f1fd316b78fe3935083f9d0.avif?t=1759166534\" width=411 height=180 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 🍖<strong>Step-by-step</strong> creation of barbecue.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 🍖 <strong>Variability</strong> of recipes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148010/extras/6cde616f860bb561b1a21db56be835b4.poster.avif?t=1759166534\" width=640 height=640 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148010/extras/6cde616f860bb561b1a21db56be835b4.webm?t=1759166534\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148010/extras/6cde616f860bb561b1a21db56be835b4.mp4?t=1759166534\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>    </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 🍖 You will <strong>smell</strong> the BBQ through the monitor</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 🍖  You can <strong>kick</strong> annoying friends who are talking about simple things</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover the art of creating barbecues from many different ingredients: even take rabbit meat and marinate it in bananas in soy sauce! (It's joke)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And by the way, don't forget to enjoy the BBQ itself after cooking!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
